Package uniol.apt.analysis.factorization

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Factorization
    A class to test if a LTS is a product.
    FactorizationModule
    Module that allows to decompose a LTS into asynchronous factors.
    GeneralDiamond
    Allows to check a LTS for the general diamond property.
    GeneralDiamondModule
    A module to check if an LTS is a T'-gdiam with a label-set T'.
    GeneralDiamondResult
    Result class for GeneralDiamond class that may contain a witness.
    LabelSeparation
    Provides methods to check if a given LTS is T'-separated for some label set T'.
    LabelSeparationModule
    A module to check if an LTS is T'-separated for some label set T'.
    LabelSeparationResult
    A result class for LabelSeparation that may also contain witness states.
    SynthesisFactorisation
    An optimized version of Factorization for the special-case of Petri net synthesis.
    TransitionSystemFilter
    A utility class that allows to modify TransitionSystems by removing certain elements.
